title: Coming Soon Television
text:
Coming Soon Television was an <a href="Italy">italian</a> <a href="Television%20channel">TV channel</a> dedicated to the world of <a href="cinematography">cinematography</a>.
On the 26 March 2014 it was replaced by <a href="Fine%20Living%20%28Italian%20TV%20channel%29">Fine Living</a>.
